reviewText: the movies are good and got a good deal

I bought it for my father in law and, although we are brazilians, i knew it would not bring a subtitle in portuguese. But, what really upset me is that they put four movies in one dvd and five, believe me, five in the other. Nine movies came in only two dvds. Although it was filmed on the 50's try to think about the image quality lose. He enjoyed anyway, and that's what really matters. He was 12 years old when he saw these movies, today he's 69. I'm happy to refresh his memories.
